      "date": "2019-10-13 17:50:06.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nThere is an \"unlinkmany -d\" option to remove directories, so I agree that this is not needed. However, could you please add the \"-d\" option to the usage message there so it is more obvious.",
