      },
      "date": "2019-10-13 17:54:22.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nProbably the same could be done with mkdirmany (in a separate patch) - it could be removed and any usage replaced with \"createmany -d\".\n\nI also have a mostly-finished patch to consolidate createmany with unlinkmany to avoid duplication of code.",
