      "date": "2019-10-14 17:59:49.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\n>Instead of killing the test, can we instead figure out why it isn't >being used in the first place and then question if we should >reimplement it?\nPetros, As Andreas pointed out it is already being used as -d option of unlinkmany binary. rmdirmany can be safely removed.",
